{"TopicId":84938,"ForumId":34,"TopicTitle":"[1.0.5] Camera Tools v1.5.1 (\u002Bdogfight mode, autozoom margin slider) - March 28","CreatedByName":"BahamutoD","CreatedById":72433,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-09-19T01:13:29Z","PageNum":10,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Fireheart318","CreatedById":159932,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-11-05T03:01:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222662239\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u002284938\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221467731919\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002272433\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022BahamutoD\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 7/5/2016 at 10:18 AM, BahamutoD said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHey everyone. \u00A0Sorry for being \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Missing in action\u0022\u003EMIA\u003C/abbr\u003E all this time. \u00A0I didn\u0027t have school or a job for the last couple years which is why I had so much time to work on KSP mods. \u00A0I\u0027ve returned to college to finish my degree, so school, work and relationships have been taking up all my time. \u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI won\u0027t be working on any of them for the foreseeable future, but their licenses permit anyone to take over if they wish. \u00A0I hope I can return one day.. I miss you all!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Cdiv title=\u0022Protected by Grammarly\u0022\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTotally understand. I look forward to the above-mentioned \u0022one day\u0022!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"jrodriguez","CreatedById":130617,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-11-09T20:37:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHi all,\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI belong to the BDArmory (Continued) development team.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m glad to announce that I just released the new version of CameraTools ready for KSP 1.2.1.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou can download the new version from:\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022https://github.com/jrodrigv/CameraTools/releases/tag/v1.7.0\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022 style=\u0022color:rgb(173,20,87);text-decoration:underline;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);font-family:\u0027Helvetica Neue\u0027, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:normal;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;word-spacing:0px;\u0022\u003Ehttps://github.com/jrodrigv/CameraTools/releases/tag/v1.7.0\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEnjoy!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Wren","CreatedById":99277,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-11-10T15:14:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nExcellent!\u00A0 This mod makes making videos so much better!\u00A0 Thanks for your hard work on this, jrodriguez!!!!\u00A0 (and the rest of the BDA team)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"mikefat","CreatedById":171417,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-11-10T21:32:57Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027v created this account just to thank you. The ksp 1.2 version has been for me by far the most stable and fps friendly and finally i will be able to make great use of this mod. Thank you again \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Wren","CreatedById":99277,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-11-10T22:09:41Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nQuick question, when we run credits and mod lists, who do we credit for